In the 1st phase, he suffers from the Morgott-syndrome: If you play by his rules and try to parry, his combos are a nightmare to parry or doge, every combo branches and looks the same to me, even after 2 hours. Now similar to Morgott, we can just overpower him there. Puppet string in his neutral state, block his combos with a heavy weapon and you are mostly fine.
